  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-05 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A VerificationActivity for iterative convergence checking is declared but no Evidence in this package carries a prov:wasGeneratedBy reference pointing back to that activity, creating an activity-evidence consistency gap (W-CON-05).",
