      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must have documented sources and uncertainty characterization; Monte Carlo UQ must cover dominant uncertain inputs.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on three input parameters (inlet velocity, blood viscosity, damage model coefficients). Wall roughness, outlet pressure waveform, and red blood cell fragility distribution were held fixed without justification. Achieved level 2."
    },
