      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Biological variability in blood samples used for experimental validation must be characterized and reported.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark data does not report donor-to-donor hematocrit variability or storage age of blood samples. Sample characterization insufficient for MRL 5 biological QoI."
    },
    {
