      "acceptanceCriteria": "Boundary conditions applied in the CFD model must be demonstrably equivalent to those measured in the validation experiment.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles in the CFD model were assumed fully developed; experimental rig inlet conditions were not characterized via PIV or hot-wire anemometry. Equivalency not established."
