    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor shortfalls relative to MRL 5 requirements, the overall assessment package is accepted for submission pending resolution of flagged epistemic gaps. The Monte Carlo UQ results and mesh convergence evidence provide sufficient basis for a conditional acceptance at this stage of the development cycle. All seven assessed factors and six not-assessed factors are documented; the iterative convergence verification activity is registered in the assurance record.",
